---
const { skill } = Astro.props;
---
<div class="v-writing-great-skills">
  <div class="wg-file">
    <div class="wg-bar">
      <span class="wg-name">SKILL.md</span>
      <span class="wg-lang">frontmatter</span>
    </div>
    <pre class="wg-code"><span class="wg-fence">---</span>
<span class="wg-key">name</span>: resolving-merge-conflicts
<span class="wg-key">description</span>: <span class="wg-hl">Use when you need to resolve an in-progress git merge or rebase conflict — hunks marked with &lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;, a halted rebase, or "unmerged paths" from git status.</span>
<span class="wg-fence">---</span>

<span class="wg-body"># Resolving merge conflicts</span>
<span class="wg-body">Reconstruct intent from both sides before…</span></pre>
  </div>
  <div class="wg-anno">
    <span class="wg-arrow"></span>
    <p class="wg-note"><strong>Triggers reliably</strong> because it names concrete situations — the <code>&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</code> markers, a halted rebase, the exact git wording — not a vague topic.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .v-writing-great-skills {
    padding: 26px; background: #faf9f6; color: #17150f;
    font-family: var(--font-sans, system-ui); border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .wg-file { border: 1px solid #d9d4c7; border-radius: 9px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.05); }
  .wg-bar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 8px 14px; background: #2b2620; }
  .wg-name { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; color: #e8e2d3; font-weight: 600; }
  .wg-lang { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8f897b; }
  .wg-code { margin: 0; padding: 16px 18px; background: #fff; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.7; color: #3a362c; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-x: auto; }
  .wg-fence { color: #b0a996; }
  .wg-key { color: #35507a; font-weight: 600; }
  .wg-hl { background: #fdf3ef; box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #e0a37c; border-radius: 4px; padding: 1px 3px; color: #6a3417; }
  .wg-body { color: #a39c8b; }
  .wg-anno { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px; padding-left: 4px; }
  .wg-arrow { flex: none; width: 22px; margin-top: 3px; border-top: 2px dashed #c0492b; height: 0; transform: rotate(-18deg); transform-origin: left; position: relative; }
  .wg-arrow::after { content: ""; position: absolute; right: -1px; top: -4px; border: 5px solid transparent; border-left-color: #c0492b; }
  .wg-note { margin: 0; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: #5b564a; }
  .wg-note strong { color: #b4552d; }
  .wg-note code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11.5px; background: #efece3; color: #7a4a2e; padding: 0 4px; border-radius: 3px; }
</style>
